<step><![CDATA[fry in ghee the cumin  and black mustard seeds,]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when done add the assafoetida and immediately after the okra]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[reduced the heat, add cayenne, turmeric, coconut, 20 mins, adding water if it's getting too dry]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[season with salt and serve]]></step>
